Pesto Veggie Burger

25 min
$8
480 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

glutennuts

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianhigh-proteinlow-calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

easyhealthyburger

Description

A deliciously hearty veggie burger packed with flavor and topped with a vibrant pesto sauce.

Ingredients

  • veggie burger patty: 2
  • whole wheat burger buns: 2
  • fresh spinach: 1 cup
  • sliced tomatoes: 1
  • sliced red onion: 1/4
  • avocado: 1/2
  • pesto sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • red pepper flakes: 1/4 teaspoon
